<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Verification Success</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: "Segoe UI", Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f5f8ff;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      height: 100vh;
    }

    .success-container {
      background-color: #ffffff;
      padding: 40px 30px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      text-align: center;
      max-width: 400px;
      width: 90%;
    }

    .checkmark {
      font-size: 60px;
      color: #28a745;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .success-title {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #333333;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .success-message {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #666666;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      background-color: #0d06d5;
      color: #ffffff;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-weight: 500;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
    }

    .btn:hover {
      background-color: #0056b3;
    }

    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      .success-title {
        font-size: 20px;
      }

      .success-message {
        font-size: 14px;
      }

      .btn {
        padding: 10px 20px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="success-container">
    <div class="checkmark">âœ…</div>
    <div class="success-title">Verification Successful</div>
    <div class="success-message">
      Doctor verification has been successfully completed. Doctor is now verified and can now explore the platform features.
    </div>
    <a href="/dashboard" class="btn">Cancel</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>